item.description: Great Smoky Mountains Half Marathon, Townsend, TN, September, 2021.

Vacation Races Grand Circle Trailfest, a 3-day trail running festival based in Kanab, UT. Three timed courses, approximately half-marathon distance each, near Bryce Canyon NP, Zion NP, and Horseshoe Bend, AZ.

Perfect size for water at work, or backyard (cocktail) trail walks with the dog. Keeps things cold, not too big that it will break your wrist trying to lift it up. The proud owner of three different colors!
Set up for my first Half Marathon
